                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110403-36-defend333 t18110403-36-punish213"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Justice Bailey.</p>
